{"tid":1939400,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論]蘭桂坊最多人最污糟既時間個場都無光, 噴光觸媒消毒有咩用？","createTime":"2020-03-23T06:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T13:20:20.000Z","uid":28729,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d97ed99702b7f6059d457824bd49c477d715977e","tid":1939400,"uid":28729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T06:21:42.000Z","msg":"飲食業界在蘭桂坊展開清潔行動<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=385360&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385360%26refer%3DShare&d=Eps995EZp4R4ibMzYmnfr4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=a9882c35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385360%26refer%3DShare&h=a4978f94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=385360&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】蘭桂坊集團主席盛智文表示，至今有至少9宗確診新型冠狀病毒個案與蘭桂坊的酒吧及食肆有關，認為數字飆升是由於部分海外返港人士不需接受強制家居隔離，預期數字將會回落，外界毋須恐慌。他認為關閉食肆不是最有效方法。 <br />\n<br />\n他們在蘭桂坊一間食肆派發納米光觸媒消毒劑，工作人員用噴劑消毒食肆的枱櫈。消毒劑會在物件表面形成保護膜，接觸光線後分解室內污染物，包括99.9%細菌及病毒，有效期達三個月。<br />\n<br />\n中華煤氣將捐贈六千支消毒劑予全港食肆。"},{"pid":"4f31156f0cac35d6686c7cf744f186f61d733eff","tid":1939400,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T06:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f701e547afb2d8fbcc9ed8bfd7e2f36fb00717","tid":1939400,"uid":225977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T06:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fe282040913a0f13b2cbb74c38ef7016f046a7","tid":1939400,"uid":226020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T06:25:45.000Z","msg":"抵班商家佬死啦"},{"pid":"d02bc189ec50117dbe47768757a91e1468945d97","tid":1939400,"uid":28729,"like":1,"dislike":0